node.text:
The Trailer!! 
“We may not be going to space, but we definitely might be going to a place where no man wants to go!”

node.text: In Capri, Italy. I believe we wore it right.

node.text: A lovey day at Disneyland. Walked pretty much 10 miles. The reason we went was to visit was to Club 33. What a kick ass experience. If you know, you know.. #happiestplaceonearth
